function.name: search_tee_times
function.description: Searches for available tee times at a golf course based on date and number of players. It returns a list of tee times along with their details such as time, course name, and availability status and the tee_time_id, booking id of the person reserving it in case it is not available.

date.description: The desired date to find available tee times in YYYY-MM-DD format.

number_of_players.description: The number of players to book for.

course_name.description: The optional name of the golf course to search for tee times.

function.name: book_tee_time
function.description: Books a specific tee time at a golf course. It returns a confirmation including booking id and status, and reason for failure in failure cases.

tee_time_id.description: The unique identifier for the selected tee time from search results.

player_details.description: A collection of details for the primary player booking the tee time.

contact_email.description: The email address for booking confirmation.

It returns a list of tee times along with their details such as time, course name, and availability status and the tee_time_id, booking id of the person reserving it in case it is not available.

date.description: The desired date to find available tee times in YYYY-MM-DD format.

number_of_players.description: The number of players to book for.

course_name.description: The optional name of the golf course to search for tee times.

function.name: book_tee_time
function.description: Books a specific tee time at a golf course. It returns a confirmation including booking id and status, and reason for failure in failure cases.

tee_time_id.description: The unique identifier for the selected tee time from search results.

player_details.description: A collection of details for the primary player booking the tee time.

contact_email.description: The email address for booking confirmation.
